column2: select a.eid,Age_at_recruitment_#,Sex_#,Ethnic_background_#,Ever_had_refractive_laser_eye_surgery_#  from dbo.Baseline_characteristics b inner join dbo.Eye_surgery_complications a       cross apply openjson(Ever_had_refractive_laser_eye_surgery_#) j on a.eid=b.eid  inner join dbo.Ethnicity e on a.eid=e.eid    where j.value in (#,#,#)
